	\\\, Veteran Resources\\\, Community Lunch. 💫\\n\\nQuestions? Contact Kari
	el at kariel@unkitawa.org\\n\\n#VietnamVeterans #Powwow #HonorOurVeterans\
	n\nhttps://unitedindians.org/event/welcome-home-vietnam-veterans-powwow/\n
